Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.30,0:22:29.93,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\pos(960,1070)\blur2}我好似被你照耀著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.10,0:22:32.52,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\pos(960,1070)\blur2}這本平凡的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.85,0:22:37.65,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\pos(960,1070)\blur2}都像是你親手遞與我的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.77,0:22:40.69,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\pos(490,1070)\blur2}在和煦微笑的你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.69,0:22:43.65,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\pos(490,1070)\blur2}我盡我所能
